## Who we help

Executive assistants, HR teams, procurement and travel coordinators who need accommodation decisions to be safe by default.

## Why companies choose Acosa

One enquiry reaches a vetted property with confirmed business essentials. No surprises on arrival, no complaints on Monday, no refund battles.

## Business Traveller Essentials™

Every listed property is assessed against the same framework, so you can compare stays on the things that matter to a working traveller.
